Create database in two ways 
1)design pattern 
  solution)right click on database open pop window wite database_name and click ok.
2)By query
  solution)create database database_name;
Note:(only Reading Knowledge)
     if you create database file.Here create two file.if you want to check thow files
     1)first which database created than go to click right go to properties and here fil path copy fil path type run command to past open 
     here seen inside two files 
     First file--->.MDF and .ldf file
     MDF(master data file(It contaains actual data file)
     ldf means Transation file log file( recover data file)
 3)If you want to rename database 
 1)right click go on rename
 2)Query by
 alter database database_name modify name=new database_name
 or(Store procedure means improve command there execute the command)
 or
 sp_renameDB old_database_name','new_databse_name;
 
 if you want to delete database 
 there two method 
 1) by graphical
 2) by query
 
 2)alter table first_table_name add contstraints first_table_name_column_name_Fk
 Foreign key(colum_name) reference second_table_name(second column_name(ex.id));
